text: Calliotropis cooperculum is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusc in the family Eucyclidae. ==Description== The length of the shell reaches 5 mm. ==Distribution== This species occurs in the Pacific Ocean off Fiji ==References== * Vilvens C. (2007) New records and new species of Calliotropis from Indo-Pacific. Novapex 8 (Hors Série 5): 1–72. ==External links== * cooperculum Category:Gastropods described in 2007
title: Calliotropis cooperculum
